title: 2 Bed/2 Bath Condo in Bloomington
posting_body: ['Available now.', 'Another new listing brought to you by The Feland Team and Renters Warehouse.', 'Located just east of the Mall of America and close to the airport, this newer building is right on the light rail line so you can commute downtown with ease.', 'This beautiful corner condo has floor to ceiling windows and a modern feel.', 'An open floor plan starts in the entry where there is a full bathroom next to a stackable washer-dryer.', 'Step into the open concept kitchen/living room space with windows all around, custom blinds, high ceilings, and hardwood floors.', 'The kitchen is spacious with an island/breakfast bar and good cabinet space.', 'The master has the same floor to ceiling windows, a walk-in closet and a full en suite.', 'The second bedroom is a good size with a large closet and the same great views.', 'The home comes with 1 underground parking spot, storage space and plenty of available outside parking.', 'Additional garage spot available for $130/month additional.', 'Amenities include a party room with a pool table-downstairs and a reading room.', 'Tenant pays electric only.', 'No pets please.', 'Please note there is a $55 application fee.', 'Also, all properties have a one-time $199 lease admin fee and a monthly processing fee of 1% of the rent.', 'This home is not currently qualified for housing assistance programs such as section 8.', 'To book a showing on this property or view the video tour, go to <URL> and scroll down to view the property of interest.']
